rol measures for S3 buckets.\n- Regular audits of S3 bucket policies and permissions.\n- Enable server access logging for all required S3 buckets.\n- Encrypting sensitive data at rest.\n\n**Log & Monitor:**\n- AWS CloudTrail logs for access and activity monitoring.\n- Enable AWS GuardDuty for threat detection.\n- AWS CloudWatch for setting up alert mechanisms.	string	\N	2025-05-07 22:30:59.6625-05	2025-05-07 22:30:59.713195-05
